content: App keeps crashing !

Doesn't deliver exactly as advertised: 1) can't recover ALL deleted files, 2) doesn't recover files deleted from external (SD card) storage, and 3) unclear how to perform a manual scan and what the Hidden Archive is. Since it can't catch all deleted files including apks, it's not a true Windows recycle bin-equivalent. Went ahead anyway and bought the paid version betting the developer will issue fixes and improvements (dynamic notification icon). So far, it's been a poor bet.
Didn't recover anything. Not even an option to recover. Just showed thumbnails. Please refund.
replyContent: Hi Josh, You can click on any thumbnail to enlarge media and then you'll see option to restore or delete. Also you can long click on thumbnails to restore multiple media. Thanks
